## 8. CURSOR SYSTEM

Use when the scenario involves a user interaction (click, hover, scroll).

**Two cursor styles available:**
- **Circular dot + ripple (pattern #14 — preferred):** Dark navy dot + white halo ring. Visible on both light and dark backgrounds. The ripple ring signals clicks. Use for all new compositions.
- **SVG arrow cursor (below — legacy):** Use only when demoing an actual OS desktop context where a real cursor matters for realism.

### SVG Arrow cursor (legacy — use pattern #14 instead)

The SVG arrow cursor with `ArrowSVG`/`HandSVG` components is no longer recommended. See pattern #14 for the current circular cursor implementation.

