## 12. FRAME-BASED SCENE ARCHITECTURE

Use when the video has distinct acts (Hero → Dashboard → Detail → CTA) rather than a single zoomable layout.

Each scene is a self-contained component that renders `null` outside its window:

```tsx
// Scene visibility pattern — every scene uses this guard
function HeroScene({ frame, fps }: { frame: number; fps: number }) {
  if (frame < TL.heroIn || frame > TL.heroOut + 20) return null;
